{"tid":280633,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(molamola) 餐飲都唔請","createTime":"2017-06-12T08:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T10:11:15.000Z","uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"797018c4c403e123e94af28ad7db77abe0df17e7","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"早排in完間cafe唔請<br />\n雖然有補習頂住 又唔係話等錢洗<br />\n但係成個暑假流流長 真係唔想做廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人究竟要幾不堪啲大型cafe先會唔請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得圍個爐取下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f4bf430bcc687e44854841e3c1f84d981474e4","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"連登成功人士個個返工忙緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a002ef5165ef214860d48442e767cbb16e1fb453","tid":280633,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"In茶記啦"},{"pid":"36d851ba7e67740f042d0e7c01e304f5baab7b6a","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>In茶記啦</blockquote><br />\n個人比較垃圾 <br />\n驚污糟/昆蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0cbb33ca43881f970acf94f05b63eb7b0ed97a","tid":280633,"uid":71662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"83deb32519ceb18b5f206bddaa0b0d63d98a8f09","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃撚圾</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c28d80d931ec086d433789f77f65c00ddca1c5","tid":280633,"uid":108628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:57:43.000Z","msg":"迪士尼<br />\nm記<br />\nkfc<br />\nstarbucks<br />\n接線生<br />\n大把pt搵啦"},{"pid":"f513e34fcd6e9cc4ba507dac58c8575607ff9d01","tid":280633,"uid":118999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>In茶記啦</blockquote><br />\n個人比較垃圾 <br />\n驚污糟/昆蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚污糟就咪撚返工啦垃圾，你一係去寫字樓做，你以為cafe就好乾淨無昆蟲好撚高級咩，你見到cafe咁乾淨，咁d污糟野邊個汁？咪係staff汁囉用下腦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3457dcea4e226a22ef2003a9cccd4722d795a9","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪士尼<br />\nm記<br />\nkfc<br />\nstarbucks<br />\n接線生<br />\n大把pt搵啦</blockquote><br />\n啱啊<br />\n等我食埋隻雞脾先去減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f1b5f733d0bba85ccaf27174f2f5bf94782044","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>In茶記啦</blockquote><br />\n個人比較垃圾 <br />\n驚污糟/昆蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚污糟就咪撚返工啦垃圾，你一係去寫字樓做，你以為cafe就好乾淨無昆蟲好撚高級咩，你見到cafe咁乾淨，咁d污糟野邊個汁？咪係staff汁囉用下腦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚污糟就咪返工 一係返寫字樓<br />\n咁返寫字樓算唔算係返緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b640f9be14c27a9e8bee6b84bae276c0b8e1f816","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>In茶記啦</blockquote><br />\n個人比較垃圾 <br />\n驚污糟/昆蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚污糟就咪撚返工啦垃圾，你一係去寫字樓做，你以為cafe就好乾淨無昆蟲好撚高級咩，你見到cafe咁乾淨，咁d污糟野邊個汁？咪係staff汁囉用下腦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚污糟就咪返工 一係返寫字樓<br />\n咁返寫字樓算唔算係返緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw抹檯個啲都接受到<br />\n係頂唔順成地屎水咁樣嗰啲樣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2f913546b416bfc62b970c19a446948c6fcc9b","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"點樣可以幫自己搵份度身定做嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗話適合興趣<br />\n可以發揮到少少長處我都好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c31fa0a204d47099e33383eb1aca9a11d2f633","tid":280633,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可以幫自己搵份度身定做嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗話適合興趣<br />\n可以發揮到少少長處我都好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n輕輕一推"}]}